Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:20.45,sign_383_2_Meet_in_4_Days,Text,0000,0000,0000,,4 Days Until \Nthe Meet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:39.03,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
