Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:42.41,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:43.51,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:44.51,Main,Daisuke,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
