Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:14.28,Main_Italics,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai once said, "People exist \Nfor love and for revolution."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:55.07,sign_4102_12_No_littering__Th,Text,0000,0000,0000,,No littering!\N{\fs14}The road is part of your yard
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:56.89,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Your time was good today, Chinatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:58.31,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the race is next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.31,0:02:59.72,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you'll make prefecturals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:00.86,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:01.83,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,You never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:03.08,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:04.72,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,You saw your time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:05.87,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.35,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,This again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.81,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:12.17,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,What flavor is yours, Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:14.21,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Kinako mochi soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.85,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Let me taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:19.84,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,It actually tastes like kinako and soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:21.85,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Literally?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:24.16,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,No, really, try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:25.47,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Can you actually tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:30.43,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Your language arts grade \Nwas good, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:32.25,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:35.73,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying you shouldn't \Ngo to the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.94,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just worried about your exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.54,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's an important time for you, Kotarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:42.68,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:53.63,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Azumi speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:56.99,Main_Italics,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kitamura of Kadoyama Publishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:59.95,Main_Italics,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your submission \Nfor the newcomer award.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.74,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Kadoyama Publishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:03.55,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:05.83,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give me a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:06.93,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:07.97,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:12.60,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:14.07,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:16.24,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Here, dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:18.07,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You made way too much, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:18.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:21.98,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:23.15,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.71,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up, Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:27.82,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:29.70,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're competing on Sunday, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:30.47,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:31.86,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be there to cheer for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.42,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.83,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:38.13,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Akane {\i1}is{\i0} a third-year now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.28,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.71,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's got a boyfriend now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:46.35,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.34,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:51.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.35,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
