Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:00.60,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:02.43,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:05.38,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:10.13,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the publisher called me and \Nsaid they wanted to meet with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.78,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.18,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:15.15,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.81,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't know what they want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.78,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You might be winning that award.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.69,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.39,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:23.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:25.57,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It really is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:28.57,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Your dream might come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:31.57,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:37.02,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but it's this Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.68,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,The same day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:42.25,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I can't come cheer for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.57,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:46.40,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,The same day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:47.27,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:49.35,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Let's both do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:54.86,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.01,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.24,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:08.79,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:10.46,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:12.70,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.60,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:14.56,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.91,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:27.75,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,The library.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:29.41,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,To study? What about lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:30.39,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:31.81,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:33.25,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:35.29,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:54.91,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
