Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:09.14,Main,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:20.83,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuno, slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.73,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:31.11,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:33.50,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bring you out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:34.33,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:40.57,sign_18176_145_Kitamura_Takeshi,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura Takeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:44.06,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,So, getting right to business...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:46.70,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an editor for ABC Publishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:50.41,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,We're searching for young writers right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:51.15,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:53.11,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,You're in middle school, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:53.88,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:56.10,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky you, being so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:13:02.79,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be honest, I don't think you're \Ncut out for serious literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:05.34,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:07.01,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,You should give up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:11.45,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, though, serious literature \Ndoesn't make any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:13.45,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recommend it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:17.70,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try \Nlight novel-type stuff instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:20.48,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling you could do it, Azumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:24.95,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be a better way to spend your \Ntime than chasing after literature awards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:26.53,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,You could get your name out there easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:30.82,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,There are tons of people who end up in their \Nthirties, still trying to become writers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:34.81,Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,You should give it a shot while you \Nstill have youth on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:44.55,sign_19686_164_Kumagaya_Sports_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Kumagaya Sports and Cultural Center
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:53.11,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,So it's just Nishio going on \Nto the semi-finals, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.11,0:13:53.76,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:56.67,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Nishio-senpai set a new personal best, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:58.92,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:06.55,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:10.12,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,What happened today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:12.36,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't focused at all, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.79,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure you could make it to prefecturals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:18.98,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Your time was actually worse than last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:21.56,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Mizuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:29.09,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,You can do better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:31.85,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,I like watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:35.40,Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,You really look like you're \Nhaving fun when you're running.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:02.14,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.00,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kotarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:12.33,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Your father told me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:14.84,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,A publisher called you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:18.25,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:22.66,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, you ought to \Nhear him out a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:26.40,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't realize the urgency of his \Nsituation because you talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:30.08,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,The festival is one thing, but \Nnothing good can come of writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.47,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:33.68,Main,Akane's dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:36.94,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there are plenty of races left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:37.52,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:39.24,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:41.37,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,"Yeah" is all you've been saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:42.52,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:43.24,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:04.39,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:05.31,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:05.98,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:17.80,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:20.95,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,My time was terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.03,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Because of your relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.59,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You know what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:29.88,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You can't keep up both at once,\Nand you end up losing both.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:30.79,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:34.56,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't focus on the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:36.48,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:43.94,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, my best friend told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:45.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.32,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That she likes the same guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:48.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:50.22,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.22,0:16:51.62,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nope, nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:53.40,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You have to ditch her, duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:54.98,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:55.64,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:59.86,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Because... my friends are important, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:03.34,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:06.45,Main,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you can stay friends with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:54.26,sign_25697_215_I_miss_you_,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I miss you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:01.26,sign_25867_216_Me_too_,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Me too
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:11.65,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:12.93,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:14.48,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:19.30,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:21.96,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:24.47,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:31.71,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I want to focus on track.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:33.42,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:36.12,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,More.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.61,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:39.96,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:43.06,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:47.55,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:50.10,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go further.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.92,Main,Kotaro,0000,0000,0000,,We promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:18:59.70,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:14.71,sign_27608_233_Schoolgirl__Daza,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Schoolgirl\N\N{\fs10}Dazai Osamu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.30,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk to you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:26.10,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:31.84,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I didn't tell you we were dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:35.40,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sorry I fell for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:39.40,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you angry, Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:40.19,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:41.60,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.94,0:19:45.19,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:46.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.25,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:49.27,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:54.35,Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,But... we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:05.51,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:11.35,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Can I confess to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:14.14,Main,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,I want proper closure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:26.08,EP Title,Chinatsu,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,1)}Run, Melos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:59.08,sign_31562_250_Sakura_s_Fantasi,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,1)}Sakura's Fantasies 1
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:04.75,Main,Roman,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.00,0:22:06.26,Main,Roman,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:06.59,sign_31787_252_Someone_you_like,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Someone you like
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.73,0:22:11.51,Main,Inaba,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! {\i1}I'm{\i0} the one who likes her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:13.51,Main,Kaneko,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, she's all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:14.21,Main,Roman,0000,0000,0000,,She's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.21,0:22:15.14,Main,Roman,0000,0000,0000,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:16.85,Main,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:19.52,Main,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:20.98,Main,Kaneko,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.98,0:22:23.11,sign_32152_261_Glasses,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.55,0:22:24.10,Main,Kaneko,0000,0000,0000,,Just give them to me, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:28.50,Main_Italics,Sakura,0000,0000,0000,,"All mine"? Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.32,0:22:32.03,sign_32352_264_Miu_and_Inaba_3,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,1)}Miu and Inaba 3
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.32,0:22:36.61,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you like about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.03,0:22:38.46,Main,Inaba,0000,0000,0000,,Everything, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:46.61,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Ryouko-sensei's so cute, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.61,0:22:47.31,Main,Inaba,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.31,0:22:48.12,Main,Inaba,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:55.80,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Try to guess what I want for my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:22:58.19,Main,Inaba,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess... A bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:02.16,Main_Italics,Inaba,0000,0000,0000,,But just last week,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.16,0:23:04.28,Main_Italics,Inaba,0000,0000,0000,,she was staring at that stuffed teddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.58,0:23:07.44,Main_Italics,Inaba,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}That's{\i1} what it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.41,0:23:11.99,sign_33313_275_Ryokou_sensei_an,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,1)}Ryouko-sensei and Roman 4
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:16.53,Main_Italics,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I have any plans, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.78,0:23:18.45,Main,Roman,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryouko-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:20.01,Main,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:22.05,Main,Roman,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'd look good in a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.47,0:23:23.83,Main,Roman,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you'd look cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:27.48,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:31.47,sign_32352_264_Miu_and_Inaba_3,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,1)}Miu and Inaba 4
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.94,0:23:33.36,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's get a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:34.47,Main,Inaba,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:35.72,Main,Inaba,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:37.75,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, sorry. From a little higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:38.31,Main,Inaba,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.31,0:23:39.88,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,No, I look ugly from that angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.88,0:23:41.13,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,A little more to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.13,0:23:42.08,Main,Inaba,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:42.63,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.63,0:23:46.37,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,From that angle, like this, \Nwith a matching pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.37,0:23:47.67,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Can you try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.29,0:23:50.22,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.22,0:23:52.00,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and the expression is important, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.00,0:23:55.77,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take the picture until I say \Nit's okay, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.51,0:24:06.37,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.37,0:24:07.54,Main,Inaba,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.61,0:24:14.13,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Ew! I can't post it on my feed \Nwith me looking like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.33,0:24:16.29,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try again, from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.29,0:24:17.36,Main,Miu,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the angle's too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:18.77,Main_Italics,Inaba,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.36,0:24:19.72,Main,Inaba,0000,0000,0000,,I might have overdone it.
